do this: hdbhatt@hdbhatt:~$ xrandr | grep " connected" | cut -f1 -d " "
gives this
DisplayPort-0 (one screen)
DisplayPort-1 other screen)



hdbhatt@hdbhatt:~$ xrandr --output DisplayPort-0 --brightness 1

hdbhatt@hdbhatt:~$ xrandr --output DisplayPort-1 --brightness 1. change this number mostly between .6 to 1 to get suitable light
